Dia. 04 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's tiger's mouth move at 1 is the proper move.
\par After White 2, Black makes an eye in the corner with 3.
\par
\par Against White A, Black B works.
\par In real game, White is going to play dansu at B, and Black lives with A.
\par
\par
